drm/i915/psr: report psr2 hw enabled from psr2_ctl

For PSR2 , as per spec, PSR2_CTL bit 31 to be set.
for psr1, bit 31 in SRD_CTL to be set. Reporting
"HW Enabled & Active bit" status for psr2 from SRD_CTL
gives  wrong status.

